


Jack is the doctor who works in this hospital.          ==> who is relative pronoun

You went to the park where i used to go.

Noruz is the day when people celebrate the new year.





        point ==> you can use "that" intead of "who,which"





I saw the woman that lives upstairs.

Are you going to buy the blouse that which(that) I chose?




        point ==> if after relative pronouns, subject come you can delete relative pronoun and it's optional.




The question was about synonyms and opposites which(that) he couldn't answer    == The question was about synonyms and opposites he couldn't answer.

I work with the man who(that) I met last year.
